section.section:
For the purpose specified in paragraph (1) of this subsection, a grant may include an award to or for:
A public or private entity;
A university researcher;
A research institution;
Private industry;
A clinical trial;
A supplement to an existing charitable or private industry grant;
A matching fund;
A fellowship in spinal cord injury research;
A research meeting concerning spinal cord injury research; or
Any other recipient or purpose which the Board determines is consistent with the purpose specified in paragraph (1) of this subsection.
